n**:\n  - While focusing on these five stocks, consider creating a diversified portfolio to manage unsystematic risk effectively.\n\n- **Correlations**:\n  - Understanding the correlations between these active stocks can guide portfolio construction. Stocks that do not move in tandem may enhance diversification benefits.\n\n- **Market Timing**:\n  - Properly timing entry points into these stocks can significantly affect potential returns. Historical price movements and pivotal market changes should be factored into decisions.\n\n### Conclusion\n\nTo formulate a successful **contrarian strategy** involving AFLT, ALRS, CHMF, GAZP, and GMKN, it’s vital to focus on identifying their unique risks and potential alpha without being swayed by prevailing market trends. This requires a robust understanding of financial theories such as alpha generation through active management, liquidity considerations, and market inefficiencies.\n\n### References\n### References\n\n- [1] Стратегия управления портфелями акций\n- [2] Оценка и управление риском\n- [3] Модели оценки доходности активов. DNA: Провести ревизию позиции по ALRS на предмет срабатывания стоп-лосса и усилить наблюдение за NVTK для фиксации прибыли при признаках разворота.. Cash: 0.74. Portfolio: [{"s":"TATN","q":4,"a":577.65},{"s":"GAZP","q":18,"a":125.614444},{"s":"ROSN","q":4,"a":436.0875},{"s":"NVTK","q":1,"a":1175.9},{"s":"ALRS","q":34,"a":31.719412},{"s":"SNGS","q":70,"a":20.383571}]. History: 13:40 BUY ROSN x1 @436.350000; 13:40 BUY ALRS x1 @31.700000; 13:35 BUY ROSN x1 @436.000000. REGIME: {"regime":"risk_on","risk":"GREEN","risk_mul":1.0,"breadth":66.667,"day":0.596,"hour":0.209,"range":1.759,"n":21}. META_CONSENSUS: []. MARKET_FEATURES: {"VTBR":{"p":94.38,"ch5":-0.053,"ch1h":-0.459,"ch1d":-1.482,"age_s":84,"trend":"mixed","issuer":"VTB","day_hi":96.8,"day_lo":93.675,"prev_hi":98.82,"prev_lo":97.6,"prev_close":97.625,"range1d":3.311},"SBER":{"p":326.59,"ch5":0.123,"ch1h":0.353,"ch1d":0.706,"age_s":84,"trend":"m